@DATABASE Catalog
@$VER: Catalog.GUIDE 1.2 (03.02.1997)

@NODE Main "Index"

	Createing new Catalogfiles for ME#?

	This is an short indroduction to create new Catalogfiles
	for the ME#? Programms.

	When you translate the CD-File please insert for the
	Gadget-Key upper-char, because the test which key is
	pressed works with upper-char (bclr #5,d0).
	Only Gadgets with to ways (Listview- and Cyclegadgets)
	becomes a lower-char.

	OK?!

	e.g.
	_Button	-> Key B	(normal Button)
	_Liste	-> Key l	(Listeview)

@ENDNODE

